Articles.Content:
So like most people I have a "junk yard". Mine is pretty much all planes so enjoy the things I deem not worthy for the forums . Actual I am to lazy to post them so I will do a single post for all the things I was to lazy to post . Some of these have been seen before but eh, most haven't so that is what counts. Keep in mind these are not as polished out as I would like them to be since it is a junk yard. Some may be unstable at times or just not fly to standards. Of course this isn't all of my junk but I don't want a flood of planes (although that would be awesome). Also there is a download for all but two so have fun! If you like any of them feel free to try it out.

Downloads

Unkerbaled scout/dogfighter AF-29

Pre WWII Fighter AF-4

Unkerbaled Attack VTOL AF-30

Post WWII Naval Fighter F9F

Strategic Bomber Air-15

You know what this one is SR-71

Just a test rover High Speed Rover
